```
## Visual Studio / .NET
## Ignore build results, temporary files, and user-specific files

# Build results
bin/
obj/
out/
Debug/
Release/

# Visual Studio cache/options
.vs/

# User-specific files
*.user
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Rider / VS Code
.idea/
.vscode/

# Logs
*.log

# Build artifacts
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb

# NuGet packages
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
packages/

# ASP.NET Scaffolding
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

# SQL Server files
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.ndf

# Test results
TestResults/
*.trx

# Coverage
coverage*.json
coverage*.xml

# Node modules (if frontend added later)
node_modules/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
